am/hrights/?cat=19&id=1000939|publisher=Tamil Canadian|date=September 2000}}</ref>}} || <ref>{{cite book|last=Rajasingham|first=K. T.|title=Sri Lanka: The Untold Story|url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/South_Asia/DI21Df01.html|chapter=Chapter 58: Premadasa indicted}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Sortname|Rohana|Kumara|nolink=1}} || ''Satana'' editor || align=center|{{Dts|1999-09-07|format=dmy}} || Pangiriwatte, [[Colombo]] || [[Colombo District|Colombo]] || [[Western Province, Sri Lanka|Western]] || Shot || [[LTTE]] || <ref>{{cite news|last=Weerakkody|first=Kalinga|title=Police now seek three-wheeler driver in \u2018Satana\u2019 editor killing|url=http://www.island.lk/2000/07/02/news.html|work=[[The Island (Sri Lanka)]]|date=2 July 2000}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Uproar in Parliament after editor's slaying|url=http://www.tamilnet.com/art.html?catid=13&artid=3899|work=[[TamilNet]]|date=8 September 1999}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Rohana Kumara|url=http://cpj.org/killed/1999/rohana-kumara.php|publisher=[[Committee to Protect Journalists]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Catch killers, if your hands are clean|url=http://sundaytimes.lk/990912/news3.html|work=[[Sunday Times (Sri Lanka)]]|date=12 September 1999}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Show's nuclear bombshell|url=http://www.thesundayleader.lk/archive/20011230/spotlight.htm|work=[[The Sunday Leader]]|date=30 December 2001}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Sortname|Nadarajah|Atputharajah|nolink=1}} (alias Ramesh) || [[Eelam People's Democratic Party]] Member of Parliament || align=center|{{Dts|1999-11-02|format=dmy}} || [[Colombo]] || [[Colombo District|Colombo]] || [[Western Province, Sri Lanka|Western]] || Shot || [[Eelam People's Democratic Party|EPDP]] || <ref name=TN160308>{{cite news|last1=Jeyaraj|first1=D. B. S.|authorlink1=D. B. S. Jeyaraj|title=Assassinating Tamil Parliamentarians: The unceasing waves|url=http://www.nation.lk/2008/03/16/newsfe1.htm|work=[[The Nation (Sri Lanka)]]|date=16 March 2008|access-date=2015-07-05|archive-url=https